name: JP3Gvault
public_notice: JPEGvaultDAO (JPEG) has rebranded to JP3Gvault (JP3G) and migrated from their older AVAX contract to a new one on Polygon. For more information, please view this post on Medium.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
JPEGvault is a DAO. A community of people who own and run it as one. Everyone benefits from its success and participates in the decision making.

Owning JPEG token provides the right to own a part of the NFT vault we are building. When we sell NFT and make benefits we redistribute them to holder according to their share of the JPEG token.
